{"tid":1407471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【8.5前密切留意「前線有共識幾點散」問題 】","createTime":"2019-08-04T15:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T04:43:03.000Z","uid":282535,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6107dfdad0802732a43492bb8163b925571f4a22","tid":1407471,"uid":282535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:28:37.000Z","msg":"以前泛民籌到錢，就用嚟請糾察跟蹤義士去篤灰。今次唔敢篤灰，但一樣可以請大堆人講「前線有共識幾點散」，叫走班和理非，等前線勇武，特別係班細路孤立無援。聽到細路無飯開就捐錢俾泛民，只會害死班細路。要捐錢請你親身去捐俾細路，唔好搵代理人，絕對唔好起大台，be water。<br />\n<br />\n#唔要大台"},{"pid":"e6758c739a6444203346075bb9eeb7a2db0250bb","tid":1407471,"uid":271539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不割蓆不分化<br />\n不用回 負皮上一頁"},{"pid":"2d68b3aab292cb2336758d612957e8304c477306","tid":1407471,"uid":282535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6758c739a6444203346075bb9eeb7a2db0250bb","tid":1407471,"uid":271539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不割蓆不分化<br />\n不用回 負皮上一頁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:43:03.000Z","msg":"事實612基金幫唔到班細食飯"}]}